---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Proven 5-Step Process | Author's Choice" description="Discover the step-by-step process Author's Choice uses to transform writers into high-earning technical writers.">
  <Header />

  <section id="process" class="process section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="process-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Our Proven <span class="text-gradient">5-Step Process</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="process-subtitle">
          From skill building to job placement, we guide you through every step of your transformation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step-card card fade-in">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Skill Training (But Only What Pays)</h3>
            <p>We skip the fluff ‚Äî no grammar drills or theory-heavy content. We focus on <strong>real-world technical writing skills</strong> like user guides, API docs, and SaaS documentation.</p>
            <ul class="step-benefits">
              <li>Hands-on projects for your portfolio</li>
              <li>Job-ready skills from day one</li>
              <li>Focus on high-demand documentation types</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card card fade-in">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Job Market Preparation</h3>
            <p>We help you <strong>build a resume and LinkedIn</strong> that positions you as a professional technical writer, even with no tech background.</p>
            <ul class="step-benefits">
              <li>Stand out to recruiters immediately</li>
              <li>Position your writing skills strategically</li>
              <li>Get noticed by hiring managers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card card fade-in">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Interview Coaching + Confidence</h3>
            <p>We walk you through <strong>mock interviews, real interview questions, and storytelling frameworks</strong> so you can pass technical writing interviews with confidence.</p>
            <ul class="step-benefits">
              <li>Practice with real interview scenarios</li>
              <li>Master the art of storytelling</li>
              <li>Build unshakeable confidence</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card card fade-in">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Mentorship + Support</h3>
            <p>You're not going through this alone ‚Äî you get <strong>access to our coach, a private community, and weekly support</strong>. When you hit roadblocks, we help you fast.</p>
            <ul class="step-benefits">
              <li>1-on-1 coaching sessions</li>
              <li>Private community of peers</li>
              <li>Real feedback on your work</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card card fade-in">
  <div class="step-number">5</div>
  <div class="step-content">
    <h3>Artificial Intelligence + Job Strategy</h3>
    <p>
      We teach you how to leverage <strong>AI tools</strong> to streamline your job search, write professional applications, and prepare for interviews. You'll also learn strategies to land <strong>freelance clients or job offers</strong>‚Äîeven if you've never written for tech before. Real scripts, AI prompts, and methods for getting noticed in today‚Äôs job market.
    </p>
    <ul class="step-benefits">
      <li>Use AI to write standout resumes, cover letters, and application materials</li>
      <li>Smart job application strategies with AI-assisted research</li>
      <li>Practice interview questions and scenarios with AI</li>
      <li>Proven outreach templates and real-world scripts</li>
      <li>Land offers or clients in 6-12 weeks</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
      </div>

      <div class="results-section">
        <h3>What Happens After the Program Ends?</h3>
        <div class="results-grid">
          <div class="result-card">
  <div class="result-icon">üíº</div>
  <h4>Unlock Income & Freedom</h4>
  <p>
    You will gain a skill no one can take away from you and one that will generate you income.<br>
    Plus, you‚Äôll be able to legally job stack to make even more money‚Äîall fully remote.
  </p>
</div>
          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">üìÅ</div>
            <h4>Professional Portfolio</h4>
            <p>Leave with a clean, professional portfolio that showcases your skills</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">üéØ</div>
            <h4>LinkedIn That Attracts Recruiters</h4>
            <p>Your profile will be optimized to get noticed by hiring managers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">üìÑ</div>
            <h4>High-Value Resume</h4>
            <p>Position yourself as a professional technical writer, not just a "writer"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">üé§</div>
            <h4>Interview Confidence</h4>
            <p>Skills and tools to pass any technical writing interview</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">üåü</div>
            <h4>Ongoing Support</h4>
            <p>Keep access to community, coach replays, and bonus tools</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-section">
        <h3>Typical Student Timeline</h3>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker">1-3</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Weeks 1-3</h4>
              <p>Complete foundational modules, start building your portfolio</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker">3-6</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Weeks 3-6</h4>
              <p>Continue building your portfolio, start networking with industry professionals</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker">6-8</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Weeks 6-8</h4>
              <p>Portfolio complete, resume polished, ready to start applying</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker">8-10</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Weeks 8-10</h4>
              <p>Begin job applications while completing final modules</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker">30-90</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>30-90 Days</h4>
              <p>Most students receive job offers or land first clients</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-cta fade-in">
      <h3>Ready to Transform Your Writing Career?</h3>
      <p>Join our next cohort and start earning what you're worth as a technical writer.</p>
      <a href="#enroll" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Join Now</a>
    </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .process {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .process-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .process-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

 .program-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .program-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes rotate {
    0% {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    100% {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  .program-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .program-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .program-modules {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .program-cta h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .program-cta p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .module-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
    }
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }

  .step-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%);
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-benefits {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .step-benefits li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .step-benefits li::before {
    content: "‚úì";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .results-section {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .results-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .result-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px var(--card-shadow);
  }

  .result-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .result-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .result-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .timeline-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .timeline-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 200px;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .step-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .step-number {
      align-self: center;
    }

    .results-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .timeline {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>